Sri Lanka cuts policy rates to reduce inflation and boost economic recovery
</h1><h2 class="sub-title">The Sri Lankan Central Bank slashed policy interest rates by 250 basis points stating it would provide an impetus for growth</h2><p class="publish-time"> June 01, 2023 01:47 pm | Updated 07:25 pm IST - Colombo </p><div class="author"><div class="author-name noimg"><a class="person-name no-lnk"> PTI</a></div></div><div class="comments-shares share-page flex print-hide" data-artid="66919025" data-title="Sri Lanka cuts policy rates to reduce inflation and boost economic recovery" data-url="https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/sri-lanka-cuts-policy-rates-to-reduce-inflation-and-boost-economic-recovery/article66919025.ece"><div class="left"><div class="share"><button class="btn share-btn" data-ga-labelclick="ArticleShare"></button><ul class="share-list " style="display: none;"><li class="copy-link" onclick="if (!window.__cfRLUnblockHandlers) return false; copytext('https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/sri-lanka-cuts-policy-rates-to-reduce-inflation-and-boost-economic-recovery/article66919025.ece');" data-cf-modified-7acd2d5d0396b5c292811a93->
